<TEXT>
   John Goodman, the husband on the television
show ``Roseanne,'' will tie the knot in real life.
   The bride-to-be is Annabeth Hartzog, a model and college student
in New Orleans. They met in October 1987 when Goodman was in
Louisiana filming ``Everybody's All American,'' Stan Rosenfield,
Goodman's agent, said Wednesday from Hollywood.
