will not announce the date. They don't want a recurrence of the
Sean Penn and Madonna incident,'' Rosenfield said.
   Reporters and photographers disrupted that wedding when they
buzzed the site in helicopters.
   Rosenfield said neither Goodman or Hartzog wanted to talk to
reporters.
