<TEXT>
   3M Co.'s said Thursday its first-quarter
income rose 15.1 percent, in part due to higher worlwide sales by
the diversified manufacturer.
   3M reported earnings of $318 million, or $1.43 a share, compared
with $277 million, or $1.22 a share, for the same 1988 period.
